headline: Stunning New Luxe Rental in Park Slope, Brooklyn: "Paseo on Fifth"
summary: Offering modern living amid brownstones, at the heart of Park Slope's Fifth Avenue corridor, the new Paseo on Fifth has officially launched leasing at the first of its two buildings, the 4-story, 49-unit 50 Paseo Place. Co-developed by William Macklowe Company and GreenBarn Investment Group through a joint venture including NTT UD USA Inc. and Rithm Capital, Paseo on Fifth honors tradition while embracing Park Slope's vibrant energy.
